### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
###  TitanChat API — Test Collection
###  Use with VS Code REST Client extension (humao.rest-client)
###  Base URL: http://localhost:8001
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8001

### ─── Health Check ───────────────────────────────────────────────

GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
###  AUTH — Admin
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Register Admin
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/admin/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@example.com",
  "password": "SecurePass123!",
  "name": "Test Admin"
}

### Login Admin
# @name adminLogin
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/admin/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@example.com",
  "password": "SecurePass123!"
}

###
@adminToken = {{adminLogin.response.body.access_token}}

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
###  BOTS
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Create Bot
# @name createBot
POST {{baseUrl}}/bots
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Website Chat Widget",
  "config": {
    "welcome_message": "Hello! How can I help you?",
    "theme": "blue"
  }
}

###
@botId = {{createBot.response.body.id}}
@botApiKey = {{createBot.response.body.api_key}}

### List Bots
GET {{baseUrl}}/bots
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Get Bot Detail
GET {{baseUrl}}/bots/{{botId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Update Bot
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/bots/{{botId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Updated Widget Name",
  "config": {
    "welcome_message": "Welcome! Ask me anything.",
    "theme": "dark"
  }
}

### Regenerate Bot API Key
POST {{baseUrl}}/bots/{{botId}}/regenerate-key
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Delete Bot (soft delete)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/bots/{{botId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
###  AGENTS
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Create Agent
# @name createAgent
POST {{baseUrl}}/agents
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "agent1@example.com",
  "password": "AgentPass456!",
  "name": "Support Agent 1",
  "skills": ["billing", "technical"],
  "max_chats": 5
}

###
@agentId = {{createAgent.response.body.id}}

### List Agents
GET {{baseUrl}}/agents
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Get Agent Detail
GET {{baseUrl}}/agents/{{agentId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Update Agent
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/agents/{{agentId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Senior Support Agent",
  "skills": ["billing", "technical", "escalation"],
  "max_chats": 8
}

### Delete Agent (soft delete)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/agents/{{agentId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
###  AUTH — Agent
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Agent Login
# @name agentLogin
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/agent/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "agent1@example.com",
  "password": "AgentPass456!"
}

###
@agentToken = {{agentLogin.response.body.access_token}}

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
###  CONVERSATIONS (requires Cassandra connection)
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### List Conversations (Admin view — scoped to admin's bots)
GET {{baseUrl}}/conversations?limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Get Conversation Detail
GET {{baseUrl}}/conversations/conv-123-example
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Get Conversation Messages (with day bucket)
GET {{baseUrl}}/conversations/conv-123-example/messages?bucket=20260528
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Get Conversation Messages (auto-scan last 7 days)
GET {{baseUrl}}/conversations/conv-123-example/messages
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
###  DASHBOARD (requires Redis connection)
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Dashboard Stats
GET {{baseUrl}}/dashboard/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Agent Statuses
GET {{baseUrl}}/dashboard/agents
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Active Chats
GET {{baseUrl}}/dashboard/active-chats
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
###  WEBSOCKET — Bot Token Auth (for reference, not executable here)
###  Connect: ws://localhost:8000/ws/{conversation_id}?bot_token={botApiKey}
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
